                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18361128-218-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18361128-218-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18361128-218-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp> for embezzlement.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18361128-name-1480" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1480" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1480" type="surname" value="HALE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1480" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HALE</persName>
                  </hi>. The prisoner was in my service. On the 2nd of No<lb></lb>vember I employed him to carry ten calf-skins to Mr. Smith's, and get the most money he could for them, and to bring it back—I saw him as more—it was his duty to have brought it if he had received it—I had dealt before with Smith, and the prisoner had been with me, but I never intrusted him to take the money before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18361128-name-1481" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1481" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1481" type="surname" value="REED"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1481" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN REED</persName>
                  </hi>. I delivered the ten calf-skins to the prisoner—he never brought the money back.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18361128-name-1482" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1482" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1482" type="surname" value="MORRISON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-1482" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH MORRISON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to Mr. Smith of Gloucester-row Locks<lb></lb>fields. The prisoner brought me ten calf-skins, and I paid him down a half-sovereign, the same price that I had given him for nine in the early part of the day.</p>
